about.body: Describe some hobbies and maybe some more personal things I am interested in.

commercial.description: Description: Applies software engineering expertise to perform in-depth technical evaluations of foreign computer and network technologies through the analysis and identification of software capabilities and vulnerabilities of specified non-US warfighting subsystems, using software program code disassembly and reverse engineering. Authors concise Scientific and Technical Intelligence (S&TI) assessments in conformance with the intelligence community (IC) analytic standards that convey the results of that analysis to the client's DoD and IC partners and clients.

Description: Developed and maintained various application components. Worked with customer end users to understand specific business requirements and develop application front end functionality. Developed knowledge with object-oriented programming language, databases, web development, JavaScript, and HTML. Provided guidance on coding standards, problem resolution, and project delivery.

Description: Supervised junior staff; Managed cash stock and inventory balances. Performed store opening and store closing duties, including counting cash drawers and checking all equipment for proper functioning.

military.description: Description: Collected and analyzed Signals Intelligence (SIGINT) to identify relevant data. Generated intelligence reports in support of US military operations. Briefed Command level staff on situational intelligence gathered from SIGINT operations.
